            <h2>Technical Requirements for Modern Websites</h2>
            <p>Modern websites need to meet specific technical standards to perform well in search:</p>
            <ul class="content-list">
                <li><strong>Core Web Vitals:</strong> Google's metrics for loading performance, interactivity, and visual stability</li>
                <li><strong>Mobile-First Design:</strong> Websites must work well on mobile devices, which Google uses as the primary index</li>
                <li><strong>Page Speed:</strong> Fast loading times affect both user experience and search rankings</li>
                <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Websites should be usable by people with disabilities and assistive technologies</li>
                <li><strong>Security:</strong> HTTPS encryption is expected for all websites</li>
                <li><strong>Structured Data:</strong> Schema markup helps search engines understand page content</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
