            <p>Effective website design balances multiple considerations:</p>
            <ul class="content-list">
                <li><strong>User Experience:</strong> Clear navigation, readable content, and intuitive interactions</li>
                <li><strong>Business Goals:</strong> Design that supports conversions and customer actions</li>
                <li><strong>Brand Identity:</strong> Visual design that reflects your business appropriately</li>
                <li><strong>Technical Performance:</strong> Code quality and hosting that delivers fast load times</li>
                <li><strong>Maintainability:</strong> Systems that allow content updates without technical expertise</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Prioritising visual complexity over these fundamentals often produces websites that look impressive but perform poorly in search and conversions.</p>
